Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺留下來的人

Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到對方竟然自己送上門來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將以這一擊 回歸那懷念的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.03,0:01:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.81,0:01:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠距離攻擊魔法 準備術式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備術式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.94,0:01:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令官 隨同部隊傳來聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里曼機關的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以第一先遣隊的指揮官為人質
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要求與司令官對話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.49,0:02:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊 在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他有話等結束再說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一先遣隊的指揮權移交給副官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續作戰行動 就這樣回覆過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等這天等得好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.98,0:02:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能被些瑣碎雜事打擾到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一擊 準備
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一擊 準備完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展開防禦魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯現吧 攔截者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Interceptor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發動攻擊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.62,0:03:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒多少時間了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有看門狗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始攻擊了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤特拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面似乎就算放棄你也要繼續作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不是工具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺身守護君主部下領民才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你玷污了我作為先鋒的榮譽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷下方中彈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,損傷確認中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何索厄拉的攻擊能擊穿我方防禦魔法?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是該我們佔優的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:03:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想來只可能是裝載的魔法思念料的差距…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續 不要減緩攻擊力度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念料的純度可是不同的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻對面陣腳大亂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討伐軍 對我們來說不過是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往首都的礙腳石而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像開打了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有魔法防壁在 應該不至於立即被擊墜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 你情況怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神支配的術式應該已經解除了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎我該道聲謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 我們也是因時勢才如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你這句話我輕鬆許多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再相遇 可以毫不顧忌地殺掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大致說明下現在情況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我基本都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有意識 也有記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵抗不住想受敵人支配的強烈欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此不舒服的感受我還是第一次經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫葛拉特的魔法師 我必須要好好謝他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 比起這事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼下更重要的是兄長和嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 肯定沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡莉也…芙蕾多妮卡也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體 回收
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回歸 和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 加瓦爾尼公爵家的人們已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 里加爾圖自身言明已把所有人殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是芙蕾多妮卡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你縮小了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我脫皮了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫皮?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是輸了一次嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.73,0:07:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我汲取教訓 把身體改為了雙重構造
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這樣保溫性也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 托魯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長往最頂層去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡也在最上面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想盡快與兄長他們匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜託你嗎 順便帶上她們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這荒唐的生物到底是怎麼回事啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中央部中彈 魔法機關受損
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法維持平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要膽怯 開炮 開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 李奧納多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊魔法失去準頭了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎發射口中彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若這樣 即使到了首都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也無法發動魔法攻擊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里加爾圖大人 葛拉特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到了個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼辦法? 告訴我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這要塞本身當作炮彈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對維馬克王宮發起突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並發動魔法自爆怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有索厄拉的魔法力在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應能將整個卡多威爾夷為平地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這主意不錯 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們自身成為新戰爭的導火索
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在歷史上留下痕跡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若維馬克王國遭遇實際上的滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個大陸都會陷入混亂的漩渦中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是蕾拉 你總會為我們指明道路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為里加爾圖大人和葛拉特大人的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉獻上一切就是我的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時 也是我的復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合軍的航天要塞已處於毀滅狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們繼續前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著首都卡多威爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 別想全身而退
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然回歸王國無望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也要拉你們一起上路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 上升
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.55,0:10:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將剩餘的功率全都使出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡 在就回話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁斷皇帝阿圖爾·賈茲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用雙手創造了歷史的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:11:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了明天 我也能與他比肩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賈茲皇帝的願望 也會由我的雙手…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了我的話 還有逃跑的力氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼想要這遺體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 原來入侵者是你們呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次見到蕾拉以外的「嘉依卡」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是里加爾圖·加瓦爾尼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你父親的信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好期待 竟有幸親手切割「嘉依卡」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停 停止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一眨眼就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要塞將突入首都卡多威爾自爆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體也好 「嘉依卡」也好 都會化為灰燼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定 放棄 否定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 會來 必定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為鋼也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 嘉依卡剛才還在這兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面就是司令室了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這群傢伙到底有多少隻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有殺過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著慢著 讓我來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得報剛才的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡 你在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像有點累?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:14:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的內臟是什麼顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 輸了?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那不是戰鬥 你只是用刀在刺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 這就是生命嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想弄明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來只要自己死一次 就能明白了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.67,0:14:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 趕緊回收遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然撞了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糾纏不休
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎負責操縱的魔法師被打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的達成了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只剩如何逃離這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:15:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:15:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍舊尋求遺體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的答覆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你接受自己工具的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就作為工具腐朽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Salimic binnu allay
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯現吧 強擊者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Slugger
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Floater
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托魯 救助成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我說多少次 亂破師只是僱主的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人為工具而冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可謂本末倒置…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.25,0:17:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否定 托魯 工具 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工具 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長 嘉依卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.37,0:18:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿卡莉 芙蕾多妮卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索厄拉 在下沉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.09,0:18:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管你幫了我們那麼多…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 里加爾圖大人和葛拉特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願意陪我復仇至今
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.61,0:19:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能成為賈茲皇帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有些累了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也累了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的活法 我的死法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我自己選的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定讓基烈特大人擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然空手而歸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是該活捉嘉依卡回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇 芷依塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.14,0:19:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咋了 怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我跟著還…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基烈特大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是在騙我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇 隊長他…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.52,0:20:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人騙人 你們騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不信 不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…你們騙人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 薇薇 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.88,0:20:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇薇!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.02,0:20:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被創造的存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.07,0:20:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若這是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼「收集遺體」本身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是某人為達到目的而設計的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 那你自己想怎麼辦啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體 收集 繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 其他沒有 什麼都
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.84,0:21:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺體 收集 想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和托魯 和阿卡莉 和芙蕾多妮卡 一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決意不變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,協助 可能?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還講這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我選你為主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.89,0:21:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你是假貨還是被人利用 這都無關
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與兄長一心同體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會追隨到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 托魯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你乾脆和我簽契約算了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若今後還要這樣亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆和我簽訂契約 成為龍騎士吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.48,0:21:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不用一一療傷了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說笑呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:21:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.37,0:21:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要出發還是趁早吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定基烈特小隊會追來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉依卡 走吧

Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新英雄 喜好葡萄酒 美魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.81,0:23:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 魔法技術 本領了得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.17,0:23:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 托魯 阿卡莉 苦戰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.32,0:23:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 敗退?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.65,0:23:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 收集遺體的皇女

